center size-full wp-image-7283\" title=\"Giá xe Ducati V4R Panigale 2019 Ducati V4R Panigale thế hệ mới ra mắt 201813\" src=\"https://xe1s.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gi%C3%A1-xe-Ducati-V4R-Panigale-2019-Ducati-V4R-Panigale-th%E1%BA%BF-h%E1%BB%87-m%E1%BB%9Bi-ra-m%E1%BA%AFt-201813.jpg\" alt=\"Giá xe Ducati V4R Panigale 2019 Ducati V4R Panigale thế hệ mới ra mắt 201813\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7284\" title=\"Giá xe Ducati V4R Panigale 2019 Ducati V4R Panigale thế hệ mới ra mắt 201814\" src=\"https://xe1s.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gi%C3%A1-xe-Ducati-V4R-Panigale-2019-Ducati-V4R-Panigale-th%E1%BA%BF-h%E1%BB%87-m%E1%BB%9Bi-ra-m%E1%BA%AFt-201814.jpg\" alt=\"Giá xe Ducati V4R Panigale 2019 Ducati V4R Panigale thế hệ mới ra mắt 201814\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></article></div>', 'Ducati Panigale V4R 2020', '', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ducati-panigale-v4r-2020__trashed', '', '', '2022-06-04 16:59:57', '2022-06-04 09:59:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/pnc/?post_type=product&#038;p=62', 0, 'product', '', 0),
